{
  "stem": "13457.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But before they transported him as a patient, he came to our tent, left us some money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So we still had food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were actually started coming to-- to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then we came to Tehran.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I'm almost towards the end, I think, of the whole saga.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "In Tehran, there were-- we lived in Polish refugee camps, with Poles.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I remember there was a-- a messenger that came out from occupied Poland, and was telling the conditions in Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And that that must have been the year '42, end of '42.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That's when the transports in Poland were going to Auschwitz and Treblinka, in full speed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he was saying how terrible it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "The Germans grabbed two or three peasant women on the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and shot them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because they thought they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother then tells-- told me-- I was a little kid.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After that she tells me, what did he say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, that they got two Poles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they shot them because they thought they were Jews?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means they are killing all the Jews there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She understood the-- the extent of the-- of what is going on, just from the-- what the guy didn't want to say, that the Jews were not even mentioned in his report.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All he was talking, was he was he was talking about the Poles.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then one day, my mother was doing her wash in sink apparently not far, of all places, of a church on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a Polish policeman came and brutalized her, beat her up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She came crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then about myself, we couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was difficult to go [? one-by-one ?] to school because the Poles were-- they're ganging up and beating us.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
